These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: dancing, card-games, singing, cooking
Sport: weightlifting, cricket, water-polo, basketball
1. Hobby:singing is between Sport:water-polo and Sport:cricket##2
2. Hobby:cooking is on the left or right of Sport:water-polo##3
3. Sport:water-polo is not to the left of Sport:water-polo##8
4. Sport:cricket != Hobby:singing##6
5. Hobby:singing is somewhere to the right of Hobby:dancing##5
6. Hobby:dancing is on the right of Sport:weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking  | dancing | singing | card-games  |
| Sport   | weightlifting | water-polo   | basketball  | cricket |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: artichoke, pineapple, kale, potato
Job: coach, musician, social-worker, fisherman
1. Job:fisherman is not to the left of Job:fisherman##8
2. Food:artichoke is somewhere to the right of Food:potato##5
3. Food:artichoke == Job:musician##1
4. Food:potato is between Food:artichoke and Food:pineapple##2
5. Food:pineapple is somewhere between Food:kale and Job:coach##7
6. Job:social-worker is somewhere to the left of Food:pineapple##5
7. Job:coach is not to the left of Job:coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | kale | pineapple          | potato | artichoke     |
| Job    | social-worker      | fisherman | coach | musician |

