.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Job: coach, dancer, police-officer, security-guard
Movie-Genre: spy, documentary, musical, horror
1. Movie-Genre:spy is not to the left of Job:police-officer##8
2. Movie-Genre:documentary is on the far left##1
3. Job:dancer is on the right of Job:coach##1
4. Job:dancer is in an even position##4
5. Job:security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
6. Job:coach is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:horror##5
7. Job:security-guard == Movie-Genre:musical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | coach | dancer | police-officer     | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | horror   | spy | musical    |

