.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
Music-Genre: country, pop, punk, reggae
Sport: tennis, handball, golf, ice-hockey
1. Sport:handball is on the left of Sport:ice-hockey##1
2. Sport:tennis is not to the left of Sport:handball##8
3. Sport:golf is on the right of Music-Genre:pop##1
4. Music-Genre:reggae is not to the right of Sport:golf##8
5. Music-Genre:country == Sport:tennis##1
6. Music-Genre:country is on the right of Sport:golf##1
7. Music-Genre:punk is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:reggae##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | pop         | reggae   | country    |
| Sport         | handball | ice-hockey | golf | tennis |

