2. Transport:snowmobile is on the far left##1
3. Transport:snowmobile is on the left or right of Music-Genre:rock##3
4. Music-Genre:trance is somewhere to the right of Transport:van##5
5. Transport:roller == Transport:roller##1
6. Music-Genre:funk != Transport:ship##6
7. Music-Genre:punk is not to the right of Music-Genre:funk##8
8. Transport:van is not to the left of Transport:roller##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | rock | funk | trance |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller       | van  | ship    |

