4. Pet:rabbit == Transport:boat##1
5. Pet:lizard is somewhere between Transport:tram and Transport:boat##7
6. Pet:lizard is on the left of Pet:snake##1
7. Transport:bus is between Transport:ship and Pet:rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | lizard | snake | rabbit |
| Transport   | tram | ship      | bus     | boat     |

 